interpretation: The anguished face emoji represents a feeling of intense distress or suffering. It may indicate a sense of overwhelming emotion, such as grief, anxiety, or fear. This card can also suggest a need for self-care or seeking support from others during a difficult time. It may be a warning to pay attention to your emotional state and take action to address any underlying issues that may be causing distress. Keywords associated with this card include pain, agony, despair, sadness, and emotional turmoil. The anguished face card can serve as a reminder to prioritize your mental health and seek help when needed.
